<TITLE> Gunman shoots lawyer in chambers </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, Aug 3 (bdnews24.com)An unidentified gunman on Monday shot a lawyer in the hand at his chamber in Kailash Ghosh Lane, police said. Mohammad Zakir Hossain, 42, was injured in his right hand in the late afternoon and was admitted to Dhaka Medical College Hospital, sub-inspector Azimul Karim, of Kotoali Police Station, told bdnews24.com. "A man entered my office and fired two shots, one of which hit me in the hand," said Hossain, who added that he suspected a man currently residing in India may have been behind the incident. Tension in the area, which houses many law chambers, has been running high since the shooting. bdn
